<L>__{interior subway station night}
<A>__{sam, all alone, walks through the station. suddenly, he reaches out and pushes a garbage can lid. it swings back and forth. he is delighted. a beer can is sitting on a bench. he pushes it off, watching it roll across the platform with childlike glee. looking up, sam sees an advertisement for market security bank and trust. he stares at it with great interest. "special banking for special people. we make it easy for you." something registers in sam's eyes. he yells and jumps straight up, hitting a subway sign with his finger. with great excitement, he runs for the stairs and rushes from the station.}
